data.description:
There’s plenty of room for everyone in this spacious Richland Park home. Downstairs boasts soaring ceilings and gorgeous hardwood floors. Kitchen is open to the large living room with vaulted ceiling and corner fireplace. Formal dining just off the two story entrance. Primary suite with double closets, soaking tub, shower and dual sink areas. A half bath and study round out the bottom floor. 

A huge gameroom with wet bar anchors the second floor with three large bedrooms and Jack & Jill bath— tons of closet space!

Close to shopping, schools and entertainment— this home is perfectly situated to enjoy the good life in Broken Arrow.
